dpkg --list apt --- shows whether the program is installed

dpkg --status apt --- package and dependency information

dpkg --listfiles apt --- list of files installed by the program

dpkg --search python* --- shows who installed the file on the system

dpkg --search README.Debian --- shows who installed the file on the system

dpkg -install name --- package installation

dpkg -i name --- package installation

apt download sudo --- tighten the package sudo

ls *.deb

dpkg --remove package_name --- removes the package

dpkg --purge package_name --- removes the package and files





















